ruling: - If you have no vacant monster zones, you cannot Special Summon with [[Enchanting Fitting Room]]. So the Level 3 or lower Normal Monsters that would be Special Summoned are sent to the Graveyard instead. All other cards are still returned to the Deck and it is shuffled.
- If you have some vacant Monster Card Zones, but not enough, select the monsters you wish to Summon with [[Enchanting Fitting Room]] and Special Summon them.
